node.text: If you haven’t gotten tickets for our Southern California Sample Sale (6/1/19) there’s still some left!! https://www.juneandjanuary.com/products/june-sample-sale?utm_medium=IGST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas with @elizabethpetteyphoto, and @brownbabesreptoo. May be an image of 1 person, child and footwear.

node.text: Back to school collection launches TOMORROW at 11am CST! Bailey will be on live today around 12:15 CST to walk us through the collection so come join.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas with @elizabethpetteyphoto. May be an image of 3 people, child and people standing.

node.text: Have you seen all the new arrivals coming Wednesday for back-to-school?! All the navy and sand you could ever want to keep them comfy even if they wear a uniform!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas with @elizabethpetteyphoto, and @amazingabigailgrace. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Introducing: The Lightweight Hoodie Dress! The basic we didn’t know we needed. This cutie style will come in Sand, Onyx, Navy, Grapefruit and Cranberry on Wednesday.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Long Island City, New York with @jessie_lea, @memonroe1, @elizabethpetteyphoto, and @tiffany.m.reeder. May be an image of 1 person, child and standing.

node.text: Add this trio to our fave color combos! Grapefruit + Fawn + Cranberry. You can preview the entire Back-to-school launch on the site right now and pick your fave color combos! Come back and tell us which ones you wanna see. Gonna gift a few outfits in the comments. 😘

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas with @elizabethpetteyphoto. May be an image of 1 person, child and standing.

node.text: Can’t even believe how much we love Moss! WOW, so glad to launch this brand new color on Wednesday. 🤩

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Queens, New York.

node.text: Looking for the best backpacks to match your basics for back-to-school?? We have gobs of Sticky Lemon options in the shop now! Did you know they’re made from recycled PET bottles?? Yup! 🙂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas.

node.text: Back-to-school basics preview up on the site now! Get a first look of all the new stuff and make your faves list. (Yep, Undies details are there too!!!)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Kids Clothes & Basics on July 22, 2021 tagging @bayandthebabes, and @sticky.lemon.

node.text: Have you heard the news? Back to school basics launch 7/28! Bailey is in the studio today and giving a behind-the-scenes look while she works so come say hi! (Oh and if you’re looking for sticky lemon back packs, we have them! Just send us a dm and we can show you what we have in stock!)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas with @bayandthebabes.

node.text: Back to basics launch is scheduled for next Wednesday! We will be sharing all the things about the release between now and then to help out with your shopping! Bailey did a bunch of color comparing on stories today, let us know if there are any others you want to see. 🙂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Kids Clothes & Basics in Austin, Texas.

node.text: All the navy and sand for the comfiest uniforms for school! Launch info coming later today so stay tuned. 🤗

node.text: In the studio today for our annual back-to-school photoshoot and gonna be sharing all the BTS in stories so COME HANG OUT and get excited with us!
